  "bio_raw": "Dr. Md. Kamal Uddin joined ULAB in May, 2023 after completing his PhD from the School of Economics and Management (\nAACSB, EQUIS and AMBA accredited\n), in Dalian University of Technology, China. Before joining ULAB, he worked as a full-time faculty in the School of Business and Economics, Metropolitan University, Sylhet. In his teaching career, he has published some original research articles in various SSCI/SCIE ranked journals including Energy Policy, Journal of Cleaner Production, Energy, and others. He is an active reviewer of different ISI ranked journals published by Elsevier, Springer, Taylor & Francis and so on.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Business, Finance and Accounting; Applied Econometrics; Energy Economics; Environmental Management; Innovation Management."
  ],
  "education": [
    {
      "raw": "Education\nPhD\n(Economic System Analysis and Management),\nSchool of Economics and Management, Dalian University of Technology, Dalian, China\nMBA\n(Major in Finance and Banking),\nShahjalal University of Science and Technology, Sylhet, Bangladesh\nBBA\n(Major in Finance),\nShahjalal University of Science and Technology, Sylhet, Bangladesh"
    }
  ],
  "publications_raw": [
